demy Award for Best Original Screenplay|Best Original Screenplay]]\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| [[Academy Award for Best Sound Editing|Best Sound Editing]]\n| {{won}}\n|\n|-\n| [[Academy Award for Best Sound Mixing|Best Sound Mixing]]\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{The Incredibles|state=expanded}}\n{{Pixar Animation Studios}}\n{{Brad Bird}}\n{{Disney franchises}}\n{{Portal bar|United States|Film|Animation|Disney|Speculative fiction}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Incredibles (franchise), The}}\n[[Category:Film franchises introduced in 2004]]\n[[Category:Comedy film franchises]]\n[[Category:English-language films]]\n[[Category:Animated film series]]\n[[Category:Pixar franchises]]\n[[Category:Children's film series]]\n", "name_user": "211.176.173.165", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "(Future Disappared)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Incredibles_(franchise)"}
