ds United A.F.C. season|2010\u201311]]\n|Championship\n|6||0||0||0||0||0||0||0||6||0\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Career total\n!282!!15!!10!!1!!12!!0!!26!!0!!330!!16\n|}\n\n===International===\nSource:<ref>{{NFT|5822}}</ref>\n\n{| class=wikitable style=\"text-align: center\"\n|-\n!National team!!Year!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|rowspan=\"6\"|[[Senegal national football team|Senegal]]\n|2001||2||0\n|-\n|2002||9||0\n|-\n|2003||7||0\n|-\n|2004||4||0\n|-\n|2005||6||0\n|-\n|2006||6||0\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total!!34!!0\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Soccerbase}}\n\n{{Navboxes colour\n|title= Senegal squads\n|bg= green\n|fg= yellow\n|bordercolor=\n|list1=\n{{Senegal squad 2002 Africa Cup of Nations}}\n{{Senegal squad 2002 FIFA World Cup}}\n{{Senegal squad 2006 Africa Cup of Nations}}\n}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Faye, Amdy}}\n[[Category:1977 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Dakar]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Senegalese footballers]]\n[[Category:Senegal international footballers]]\n[[Category:Senegalese expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in France]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in England]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Scotland]]\n[[Category:\u00c9toile Fr\u00e9jus Saint-Rapha\u00ebl players]]\n[[Category:AS Monaco FC players]]\n[[Category:AJ Auxerre players]]\n[[Category:Portsmouth F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Newcastle United F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Charlton Athletic F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Rangers F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Stoke City F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Leeds United F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Ligue 1 players]]\n[[Category:Premier League players]]\n[[Category:Senegalese expatriate sportspeople in England]]\n[[Category:Scottish Premier League players]]\n[[Category:English Football League players]]\n[[Category:2002 FIFA World Cup players]]\n[[Category:2002 African Cup of Nations players]]\n[[Category:2006 Africa Cup of Nations players]]\n[[Category:Faye 